      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is this E46 M3, a definitive driver\u2019s platform featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This power unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized volumetric efficiency across the rev range. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and delivered through a limited-slip differential. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe mounting points have been reinforced, addressing a known chassis harmonic issue. Recent technical service includes a comprehensive valve shim adjustment and a cooling system overhaul with a high-flow water pump. The suspension maintains its factory kinematics, providing the precise turn-in and lateral stability expected of the M-chassis. A mechanically robust specimen ready for spirited operation.",
      "price": 34500.0,
